originalText.text: I had the pleasure of meeting Yiska a few months ago through work. I was amazed to meet such a nice and warm person. However it is only when I visited her as a client yesterday that I truly experienced how gifted she is. I arrived completely blocked and with her magical hands, I felt like  a new person in just one hour. She helps healing your body and your mind! A beautiful soul with incredible healing skills! I cannot recommend her enough!
